Generate a tidy table with the results of DESeq

Source: R/deseqresult2tbl.R
deseqresult2tbl.Rd

Generate a tidy table with the results of DESeq

Usage

deseqresult2tbl(res_de)

Arguments

res_de

A DESeqResults object

Value

A "tidy" data.frame with all genes

Examples


# with simulated data...
library(DESeq2)
data(res_de_macrophage, package = "mosdef")
deseqresult2tbl(res_macrophage_IFNg_vs_naive)
